                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/4785" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">HRM-0381</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8834 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">ZJ 城建院公司的绩效管理体系</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The Performance Management System in ZJ Urban Planning and Design Institute Company</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">吴文华，何燕珍，曹明，周柏利</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">厦门大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中交城乡建设规划设计研究院有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">交通运输业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">生产运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">21 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">绩效管理；绩效考核；关键绩效指标法（KPI）；员工激励</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Performance Management  ; Performance Rating; Key Performance Indicator(KPI) ; Employee Incentive Mechanism</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">ZJ城建院公司是一家大型国有设计院集团的子公司，主要从事公路、桥梁、隧道设计以及城市、交通等的规划与设计业务。该公司技术平台好、项目资源丰富，聚集了一批高素质的设计、规划等专业技术人才，近年来公司呈现出快速发展的态势。与此同时，员工激励不足已成为制约公司进一步做大做强的绊脚石，公司决定以绩效管理体系重塑为抓手，优化公司管理，激励员工，促进公司持续发展。据此，本案例重点描述了ZJ城建院抓住公司发展的大好时机，在明确公司各部门职责的基础上完善各岗位的工作说明书，从绩效计划、绩效辅导与沟通、绩效考核与反馈以及绩效结果的应用等方面分析诊断公司绩效管理问题、以目标管理法和关键绩效指标法等重构公司各层次绩效考核指标体系、进而优化整个公司绩效管理体系的具体过程。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">ZJ Urban Planning and Design Institute Company is a subsidiary of a large state-owned design institute group, mainly engaged in highway, bridge, tunnel design and urban, traffic planning and design business. The company has a good technology platform, rich project resources, and has gathered a number of high-quality design, planning and other professional technical personnel. In recent years, the company has shown a trend of rapid development. At the same time, the lack of employee incentive has become a stumbling block to the company&#39;s further development. The company decided to take the remolding of performance management system as the starting point to optimize the company&#39;s management, innovate employees and promote the sustainable development of the company. Accordingly, this case focuses on describing the specific process of ZJ Urban Construction Institute to analyze and diagnose the performance management problems of the company, reconstruct the performance assessment indicator system at all levels of the company with target management method and key performance indicator method, and finally optimize the whole performance management system of the company.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2019</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《人力资源管理》 、《绩效与薪酬管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">战略性绩效管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020-10</td>
                            </tr>
